      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NAN SAID NO (1) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 2.25 lengths (17.99). Has placed several times at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Should be very hard to beat this time. ZHANG (2) is better than last start when sixth (30.66) in a Grade 5 at Richmond over 520m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Must be included in calculations. ANJO STATUE (4) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 17.79 beating Bad Boy Jay. Awkwardly drawn but has a good record over this journey. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up again.",
